description: Taste of Soul Egg Roll is the biggest baddest egg roll truck ever! Serving up delicious hand rolled egg rolls for breakfast, lunch/dinner, and dessert! Oh yea don't forget our chicken fried rice aka soul rice!Tired of eating the same old food? Come experience the best egg rolls around! Taste of Soul Egg Roll food truck offers mouth watering egg rolls and rice. We have created an unbelievable flavorful deep fried egg roll stuffed with ground turkey and vegetables. Our signature Soul rice has seasoned chicken breast and is sure to please. Hungry yet? Don't just put us off until lunch or dinner. We serve breakfast too! Try our bacon, hash brown and cheese or sausage, hash brown and cheese egg rolls!
name: Taste of Soul Egg Roll
